name: 150 Million Spheres
description: A collection of frames from the Spheres/Moon project: renders of innumerable spheres, approximately 1,024,000 visible here per layer of colour; overlays allowed; detritus from previous renders still visible. Render time is considerable, possibly due to inconsistencies and redundancy in the rendering code. Processing handles the rendering; ImageMagick provides post-render stitching courtesy.
